# Citadel SaaS Factory — Cursor Rules

> **Canonical context**: `context.md` at repository root — all architecture, standards, conventions, and agent system details.

## Key Rules

- Immutability by default — create new objects, never mutate
- Small files (200-400 lines, 800 max), small functions (<50 lines)
- TDD mandatory (80% coverage)
- Conventional commits: feat, fix, refactor, docs, test, chore, perf, ci
- Clean architecture: domain > use cases > interfaces > infrastructure
- No hardcoded secrets — use env vars or Vault
- Parameterized queries only
- Rate limiting on all endpoints
- WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility
- All LLM output passes through guardrails validation

## Multi-Model

Model routing defined in `models/routing.yaml`. Tiers: reasoning_deep, reasoning_fast, cheap_fast, long_context, code_specialist, vision, local_only, ultra_context, reasoning_chain.

